      "author": "ShawnSomething",
      "description": "Initial release of GCal Sidebar, a Google Calendar sidebar plugin for Obsidian.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n- Multi-account Google Calendar support via OAuth 2.0\r\n- Bi-directional sync (drag-to-move, edit, create, delete)\r\n- Accept / decline / tentative RSVP for invites\r\n- Day / 3-day / Week views with mini month navigation\r\n- Recurring event support",
      "downloadCount": 1,
